---
title: Pork Basil Stir-Fry over Jade Rice with Green Beans and Crushed Peanuts
description: We can’t decide which part of this dish we like best. Is it the ground pork topped with peanuts and spiked with aromatic basil and a few squeezes of lime? Or what about the jade rice with its stunning green hue and vanilla aroma? Maybe it’s the roasted green beans, with their satisfying veggie crispness. No matter which, they all come together to create symphony of flavor.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-basil-stir-fry-6d63a9ea.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/pork-basil-stir-fry-5aaac487ae08b5557c3910d2-1ff49f93.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: Thai
nutrition:
  calories: 790 kcal
  fat: 40 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
  carbohydrates: 73 g
  sugar: 7 g
  protein: 36 g
  fiber: 8 g
  sodium: 360 mg
time required: 35 minutes
course: main course
